  <entry>
    <title>React 性能优化实战指南</title>
    <url>/dev-blog/2026/06/20/react-performance-optimization/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>随着 React 应用规模增长，性能问题逐渐显现。本文将结合实际场景，介绍几种常用且高效的 React 性能优化手段，帮助你构建更流畅的用户体验。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="一、useMemo：缓存昂贵计算"><a href="#一、useMemo：缓存昂贵计算" class="headerlink" title="一、useMemo：缓存昂贵计算"></a>一、useMemo：缓存昂贵计算</h2><p>当组件中存在耗时计算时，每次渲染都会重复执行。<code>useMemo</code> 可以缓存计算结果，仅在依赖项变化时重新计算。</p>
<figure class="highlight tsx"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; useMemo, useState &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;react&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">PriceList</span>(<span class="params">&#123; items &#125;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> [keyword, setKeyword] = <span class="title function_">useState</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> [count, setCount] = <span class="title function_">useState</span>(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 昂贵的筛选计算，仅依赖 items 和 keyword</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> filtered = <span class="title function_">useMemo</span>(<span class="function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> items.<span class="title function_">filter</span>(<span class="function"><span class="params">item</span> =&gt;</span> item.<span class="property">name</span>.<span class="title function_">includes</span>(keyword))</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;, [items, keyword])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> (</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&#123;keyword&#125;</span> <span class="attr">onChange</span>=<span class="string">&#123;e</span> =&gt;</span> setKeyword(e.target.value)&#125; /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">onClick</span>=<span class="string">&#123;()</span> =&gt;</span> setCount(c =&gt; c + 1)&#125;&gt;点击 &#123;count&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">      &#123;filtered.map(item =&gt; <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">key</span>=<span class="string">&#123;item.id&#125;</span>&gt;</span>&#123;item.name&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span>)&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">  )</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>上面的例子中，即使 <code>count</code> 变化触发组件重渲染，<code>filtered</code> 也不会重新计算，因为依赖项 <code>items</code> 和 <code>keyword</code> 未变。</p>
<h2 id="二、useCallback：稳定函数引用"><a href="#二、useCallback：稳定函数引用" class="headerlink" title="二、useCallback：稳定函数引用"></a>二、useCallback：稳定函数引用</h2><p>将函数作为 props 传递给子组件时，每次父组件渲染都会生成新函数，导致子组件无谓重渲染。<code>useCallback</code> 可保持函数引用稳定。</p>
<figure class="highlight tsx"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; useCallback, useState &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;react&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">Parent</span>(<span class="params"></span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> [count, setCount] = <span class="title function_">useState</span>(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> handleClick = <span class="title function_">useCallback</span>(<span class="function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;按钮被点击&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;, [])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Child</span> <span class="attr">onClick</span>=<span class="string">&#123;handleClick&#125;</span> <span class="attr">count</span>=<span class="string">&#123;count&#125;</span> /&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title class_">Child</span> = <span class="title class_">React</span>.<span class="title function_">memo</span>(<span class="function">(<span class="params">&#123; onClick &#125;</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;子组件渲染&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">onClick</span>=<span class="string">&#123;onClick&#125;</span>&gt;</span>子按钮<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="三、React-memo：跳过无变化渲染"><a href="#三、React-memo：跳过无变化渲染" class="headerlink" title="三、React.memo：跳过无变化渲染"></a>三、React.memo：跳过无变化渲染</h2><p><code>React.memo</code> 是高阶组件，仅在 props 发生变化时才重新渲染，适合纯展示组件。</p>
<figure class="highlight tsx"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title class_">UserCard</span> = <span class="title class_">React</span>.<span class="title function_">memo</span>(<span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">UserCard</span>(<span class="params">&#123; name, avatar &#125;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> (</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">className</span>=<span class="string">&quot;card&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&#123;avatar&#125;</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">&#123;name&#125;</span> /&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span>&#123;name&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">  )</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>注意：<code>React.memo</code> 默认做浅比较。若 props 含对象或函数，需配合 <code>useMemo</code>&#x2F;<code>useCallback</code> 才能真正生效。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="四、虚拟列表：长列表渲染利器"><a href="#四、虚拟列表：长列表渲染利器" class="headerlink" title="四、虚拟列表：长列表渲染利器"></a>四、虚拟列表：长列表渲染利器</h2><p>渲染上千条数据时，全量渲染会导致明显卡顿。虚拟列表只渲染可视区域内的元素，常见库有 <code>react-window</code>、<code>react-virtualized</code>。</p>
<figure class="highlight tsx"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; <span class="title class_">FixedSizeList</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="title class_">List</span> &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;react-window&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">Row</span> = (<span class="params">&#123; index, style &#125;</span>) =&gt; (</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&#123;style&#125;</span>&gt;</span>第 &#123;index&#125; 行<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">BigList</span>(<span class="params"></span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> (</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">List</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag"><span class="language-xml">      <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&#123;400&#125;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag"><span class="language-xml">      <span class="attr">itemCount</span>=<span class="string">&#123;10000&#125;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag"><span class="language-xml">      <span class="attr">itemSize</span>=<span class="string">&#123;35&#125;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag"><span class="language-xml">      <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&#123;300&#125;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag"><span class="language-xml">    &gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">      &#123;Row&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">List</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">  )</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>使用虚拟列表后，无论数据量多大，DOM 节点数都保持在几十个量级，滚动丝滑流畅。</p>
<h2 id="五、代码分割：按需加载"><a href="#五、代码分割：按需加载" class="headerlink" title="五、代码分割：按需加载"></a>五、代码分割：按需加载</h2><p>使用 <code>React.lazy</code> 与 <code>Suspense</code> 实现路由级或组件级懒加载，减小首屏体积。</p>
<figure class="highlight tsx"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; lazy, <span class="title class_">Suspense</span> &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;react&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title class_">Dashboard</span> = <span class="title function_">lazy</span>(<span class="function">() =&gt;</span> <span class="keyword">import</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;./pages/Dashboard&#x27;</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">App</span>(<span class="params"></span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> (</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Suspense</span> <span class="attr">fallback</span>=<span class="string">&#123;</span>&lt;<span class="attr">div</span>&gt;</span>加载中...<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span>&#125;&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Dashboard</span> /&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">Suspense</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">  )</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>配合路由使用时，用户访问某路由才会加载对应 chunk，显著缩短首屏加载时间。</p>
<h2 id="六、其他建议"><a href="#六、其他建议" class="headerlink" title="六、其他建议"></a>六、其他建议</h2><ul>
<li><strong>避免在 render 中创建新对象</strong>：将常量对象提到组件外，防止引用变化。</li>
<li><strong>合理使用 key</strong>：列表项使用稳定唯一 key，避免用数组索引，防止状态错乱。</li>
<li><strong>使用 React DevTools Profiler</strong>：定位真实瓶颈，避免盲目优化。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>性能优化没有银弹，应遵循”测量—定位—优化”的流程。<code>useMemo</code>、<code>useCallback</code>、<code>React.memo</code>、虚拟列表、代码分割是最常用的工具组合，结合 Profiler 分析，才能让优化有的放矢，避免过早优化带来的代码复杂度上升。</p>
]]></content>
