  <entry>
    <title>TypeScript 高级类型详解</title>
    <url>/dev-blog/2026/06/15/typescript-advanced-types/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>TypeScript 的类型系统远不止基础类型与接口，它强大的高级类型能力让我们可以编写出更安全、更具表达力的代码。本文介绍几种常用的高级类型用法。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="一、条件类型"><a href="#一、条件类型" class="headerlink" title="一、条件类型"></a>一、条件类型</h2><p>条件类型形如三元表达式，根据输入类型动态决定输出类型，是构建工具类型的基础。</p>
<figure class="highlight ts"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">IsString</span>&lt;T&gt; = T <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="built_in">string</span> ? <span class="literal">true</span> : <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> A = <span class="title class_">IsString</span>&lt;<span class="string">&#x27;hello&#x27;</span>&gt; <span class="comment">// true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> B = <span class="title class_">IsString</span>&lt;<span class="number">123</span>&gt;     <span class="comment">// false</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 实用示例：剔除 null 与 undefined</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">NonNullable</span>&lt;T&gt; = T <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="literal">null</span> | <span class="literal">undefined</span> ? <span class="built_in">never</span> : T</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> C = <span class="title class_">NonNullable</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">string</span> | <span class="literal">null</span>&gt; <span class="comment">// string</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>条件类型在分布特性下会对联合类型逐个判断，非常适合做类型过滤。</p>
<h2 id="二、映射类型"><a href="#二、映射类型" class="headerlink" title="二、映射类型"></a>二、映射类型</h2><p>映射类型可以基于已有类型按规则生成新类型，常用于批量修改属性。</p>
<figure class="highlight ts"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">ReadOnly</span>&lt;T&gt; = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">readonly</span> [K <span class="keyword">in</span> keyof T]: T[K]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">Optional</span>&lt;T&gt; = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  [K <span class="keyword">in</span> keyof T]?: T[K]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">interface</span> <span class="title class_">User</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">id</span>: <span class="built_in">number</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name</span>: <span class="built_in">string</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">email</span>: <span class="built_in">string</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">ReadOnlyUser</span> = <span class="title class_">ReadOnly</span>&lt;<span class="title class_">User</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &#123; readonly id: number; readonly name: string; readonly email: string &#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>TypeScript 内置的 <code>Readonly&lt;T&gt;</code>、<code>Partial&lt;T&gt;</code>、<code>Pick&lt;T,K&gt;</code>、<code>Omit&lt;T,K&gt;</code> 都基于映射类型实现，日常开发中可以直接使用。</p>
<h2 id="三、infer-关键字"><a href="#三、infer-关键字" class="headerlink" title="三、infer 关键字"></a>三、infer 关键字</h2><p><code>infer</code> 用于在条件类型中”推断”并提取某个类型变量，是提取函数返回值、数组元素、Promise 值等类型的关键。</p>
<figure class="highlight ts"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 提取函数返回值类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">ReturnType</span>&lt;T&gt; = T <span class="title function_">extends</span> (...<span class="attr">args</span>: <span class="built_in">any</span>[]) =&gt; infer R ? R : <span class="built_in">never</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 提取 Promise 的值类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">Unpacked</span>&lt;T&gt; = T <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title class_">Promise</span>&lt;infer U&gt; ? U : T</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 提取数组元素类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">ItemOf</span>&lt;T&gt; = T <span class="title function_">extends</span> (infer I)[] ? I : <span class="built_in">never</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="variable constant_">R1</span> = <span class="title class_">ReturnType</span>&lt;<span class="function">() =&gt;</span> <span class="built_in">string</span>&gt;   <span class="comment">// string</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="variable constant_">R2</span> = <span class="title class_">Unpacked</span>&lt;<span class="title class_">Promise</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">number</span>&gt;&gt;  <span class="comment">// number</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="variable constant_">R3</span> = <span class="title class_">ItemOf</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">string</span>[]&gt;           <span class="comment">// string</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><code>infer</code> 让类型具备了”模式匹配”的能力，是编写复杂工具类型的利器。</p>
<h2 id="四、模板字面量类型"><a href="#四、模板字面量类型" class="headerlink" title="四、模板字面量类型"></a>四、模板字面量类型</h2><p>模板字面量类型让我们可以对字符串进行类型层面的拼接与约束，配合 <code>infer</code> 还能实现字符串解析。</p>
<figure class="highlight ts"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">Greeting</span> = <span class="string">`hello <span class="subst">$&#123;<span class="built_in">string</span>&#125;</span>`</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="attr">g</span>: <span class="title class_">Greeting</span> = <span class="string">&#x27;hello world&#x27;</span> <span class="comment">// OK</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// const bad: Greeting = &#x27;hi world&#x27; // 报错</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 提取对象中以 on 开头的属性名</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">ExtractKeys</span>&lt;T&gt; = keyof T &amp; <span class="string">`on<span class="subst">$&#123;<span class="built_in">string</span>&#125;</span>`</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">interface</span> <span class="title class_">Events</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">onClick</span>: <span class="function">() =&gt;</span> <span class="built_in">void</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">onHover</span>: <span class="function">() =&gt;</span> <span class="built_in">void</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">value</span>: <span class="built_in">number</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">Handlers</span> = <span class="title class_">ExtractKeys</span>&lt;<span class="title class_">Events</span>&gt; <span class="comment">// &#x27;onClick&#x27; | &#x27;onHover&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="五、综合示例：Getter-类型生成器"><a href="#五、综合示例：Getter-类型生成器" class="headerlink" title="五、综合示例：Getter 类型生成器"></a>五、综合示例：Getter 类型生成器</h2><p>结合映射类型、<code>infer</code> 与模板字面量类型，可以自动生成 getter 方法签名，实现类型层面的代码生成。</p>
<figure class="highlight ts"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">Getters</span>&lt;T&gt; = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  [K <span class="keyword">in</span> keyof T <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="string">`get<span class="subst">$&#123;Capitalize&lt;<span class="built_in">string</span> &amp; K&gt;&#125;</span>`</span>]: <span class="function">() =&gt;</span> T[K]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">interface</span> <span class="title class_">Person</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name</span>: <span class="built_in">string</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">age</span>: <span class="built_in">number</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">PersonGetters</span> = <span class="title class_">Getters</span>&lt;<span class="title class_">Person</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &#123; getName: () =&gt; string; getAge: () =&gt; number &#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这里 <code>as</code> 子句对键进行了重映射，<code>Capitalize</code> 是内置工具类型，将首字母大写。</p>
<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>TypeScript 高级类型让类型系统具备了”计算”能力：条件类型实现分支判断，映射类型实现批量转换，<code>infer</code> 实现类型提取，模板字面量类型实现字符串约束。掌握这些工具，能让你的工具类型库更强大，业务代码更健壮，并在编译阶段就捕获大量潜在错误。</p>
]]></content>
