    <title>Docker 前端项目部署指南</title>
    <url>/dev-blog/2026/06/10/docker-deployment-guide/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>将前端项目容器化部署，可以保证环境一致性、便于版本回滚与横向扩展。本文以一个 React&#x2F;Vue 构建产物为例，介绍完整的 Docker 部署方案。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="一、基础-Dockerfile"><a href="#一、基础-Dockerfile" class="headerlink" title="一、基础 Dockerfile"></a>一、基础 Dockerfile</h2><p>最简单的思路是构建后用 nginx 托管静态文件。但单阶段构建会让最终镜像包含 node_modules 等无用文件，体积臃肿。因此推荐使用多阶段构建。</p>
<figure class="highlight dockerfile"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span> node:<span class="number">18</span>-alpine AS build</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">WORKDIR</span><span class="language-bash"> /app</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> package*.json ./</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">RUN</span><span class="language-bash"> npm ci</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> . .</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">RUN</span><span class="language-bash"> npm run build</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span> nginx:alpine</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> --from=build /app/dist /usr/share/nginx/html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">EXPOSE</span> <span class="number">80</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CMD</span><span class="language-bash"> [<span class="string">&quot;nginx&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;-g&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;daemon off;&quot;</span>]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="二、多阶段构建说明"><a href="#二、多阶段构建说明" class="headerlink" title="二、多阶段构建说明"></a>二、多阶段构建说明</h2><p>上面的示例已使用多阶段构建：第一阶段 <code>build</code> 负责 npm install 与打包，第二阶段 <code>nginx</code> 仅包含静态产物。这样最终镜像体积可从 1GB+ 降到 30MB 左右。</p>
<p>构建与运行命令：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker build -t my-frontend:1.0 .</span><br><span class="line">docker run -d -p 8080:80 --name web my-frontend:1.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>访问 <code>http://localhost:8080</code> 即可看到页面。</p>
<h2 id="三、Nginx-配置"><a href="#三、Nginx-配置" class="headerlink" title="三、Nginx 配置"></a>三、Nginx 配置</h2><p>前端单页应用（SPA）需要把所有路由回退到 <code>index.html</code>，否则刷新页面会 404。自定义 <code>nginx.conf</code>：</p>
<figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">server</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">listen</span>       <span class="number">80</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">server_name</span>  _;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">root</span>   /usr/share/nginx/html;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">index</span>  index.html;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># SPA 路由回退</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="section">location</span> / &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">try_files</span> <span class="variable">$uri</span> <span class="variable">$uri</span>/ /index.html;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 静态资源长缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="section">location</span> <span class="regexp">~* \.(js|css|png|jpg|svg|woff2)$</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">expires</span> <span class="number">30d</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">add_header</span> Cache-Control <span class="string">&quot;public, immutable&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># gzip 压缩</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">gzip</span> <span class="literal">on</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">gzip_types</span> text/css application/javascript application/json image/svg+xml;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">gzip_min_length</span> <span class="number">1024</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>将配置一并拷入镜像：</p>
<figure class="highlight dockerfile"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span> nginx:alpine</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> --from=build /app/dist /usr/share/nginx/html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> nginx.conf /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="四、-dockerignore"><a href="#四、-dockerignore" class="headerlink" title="四、.dockerignore"></a>四、.dockerignore</h2><p>避免把本地依赖和构建产物拷入镜像，加速构建并减小上下文体积：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node_modules</span><br><span class="line">dist</span><br><span class="line">.git</span><br><span class="line">*.log</span><br><span class="line">.vscode</span><br><span class="line">.env</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="五、docker-compose-编排"><a href="#五、docker-compose-编排" class="headerlink" title="五、docker-compose 编排"></a>五、docker-compose 编排</h2><p>实际部署往往需要前端与后端 API 联动，使用 <code>docker-compose</code> 可一键拉起多个服务：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">version:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;3.8&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">services:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">web:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">build:</span> <span class="string">.</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">my-frontend:1.0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&quot;8080:80&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">restart:</span> <span class="string">unless-stopped</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">depends_on:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">api</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">api:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">my-backend:1.0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&quot;3000:3000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">environment:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">NODE_ENV=production</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">restart:</span> <span class="string">unless-stopped</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>启动：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker-compose up -d --build</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><code>--build</code> 会在启动前重新构建镜像，<code>-d</code> 表示后台运行。</p>
<h2 id="六、CI-CD-小贴士"><a href="#六、CI-CD-小贴士" class="headerlink" title="六、CI&#x2F;CD 小贴士"></a>六、CI&#x2F;CD 小贴士</h2><ul>
<li><strong>利用 Docker 层缓存</strong>：先 <code>COPY package*.json</code> 再 <code>npm ci</code>，依赖不变时跳过安装步骤。</li>
<li><strong>镜像标签策略</strong>：使用 git commit hash 作为标签，便于回滚到任意版本。</li>
<li><strong>推送与拉取</strong>：推送到镜像仓库后，服务器只需 <code>docker pull &amp;&amp; docker-compose up -d</code> 即可完成更新。</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker tag my-frontend:1.0 registry.example.com/my-frontend:1.0</span><br><span class="line">docker push registry.example.com/my-frontend:1.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>多阶段构建 + nginx 托管静态文件，是前端容器化的标准做法。配合 <code>.dockerignore</code>、自定义 nginx 配置和 docker-compose 编排，可以搭建出轻量、稳定、易于维护的部署流水线，让前端部署从此告别”在我电脑上是好的”。</p>
]]></content>
